Package org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain

Class FattyAcid

java.lang.Object
org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.FunctionalGroup
org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.FattyAcid
Direct Known Subclasses:
LipidSpeciesInfo
public class FattyAcid extends FunctionalGroup
A fatty acid with a specific type. This object defines the name, position, number of carbon atoms, hydroxyls and double bonds, as well as the bond type to the head group. A FattyAcid can carry optional modifications / functional groups and can report double bond positions.
Author:
Dominik Kopczynski, Nils Hoffmann
